title: Nikki Haley says challenging Trump is more important than ever
description: With just days to go before South Carolina's crucial Republican primary, Nikki Haley is making the case for her continued candidacy for the Republican nomination

title: I asked about race on reality shows at the TV critics press tour. It didn't go well.
description: What's ahead for the TV industry in 2024? Original series are down 14% but it still feels like too much TV. Executives and streaming services are feeling the squeeze post strikes. Race issues persist.

title: WikiLeaks founder Assange starts final legal battle to avoid extradition to U.S.
description: Julian Assange's lawyers will begin their final U.K. legal challenge on Tuesday to stop the WikiLeaks founder from being sent to the United States to face spying charges.

title: Wife of assassinated Haitian president is indicted in his killing
description: A judge in Haiti probing the 2021 assassination of President Jovenel Moïse indicted his widow, Martine Moïse, ex-prime minister Claude Joseph and the ex-chief of Haiti's National Police, Léon Charles.

title: Capital One is acquiring Discover in a deal worth $35 billion
description: The companies are teaming up, in part, to expand their payment network. Discover is the smallest of the four U.S.-based payment networks, which also include Visa, American Express and Mastercard.
